<P>Published <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> the Act direct<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">. by J. Dodsley in Pall Mall June 26&punc; 1780.</P>
